227
00:12:57,540 --> 00:13:00,750
毕竟你检举过民主党的总统
After all, you prosecuted a Democratic president.

228
00:13:00,810 --> 00:13:03,080
当副检察长屈才了
You're too good to be Solicitor General.

229
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:06,480
你要拿稳这个铁饭碗
Let's make sure you have a job for life.

230
00:13:07,570 --> 00:13:09,440
