Thank you, Mr. President.

242
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:21,350
你看到了吗
Did you see this?

243
00:14:22,270 --> 00:14:22,860
看到什么
See what?

244
00:14:23,880 --> 00:14:25,180
我刚收到警告了
I just got an alert.

245
00:14:26,220 --> 00:14:28,760
不知道  我好一阵没见到吉姆了
I don't know. I haven't, uh... seen Jim in a while.

246
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:32,180
真奇怪
That's weird.

247
00:14:41,280 --> 00:14:43,850
