is lower than it's ever been.

260
00:15:16,040 --> 00:15:17,920
这些数字是假的
Those numbers are false.

261
00:15:17,920 --> 00:15:21,510
2010年只死了一个平民  肯定不对
One civilian killed in 2010? That has to be wrong.

262
00:15:21,510 --> 00:15:24,840
听着  我不认为五角大楼对此说了实话
Look, I don't think the Pentagon is being honest about--

263
00:15:29,930 --> 00:15:30,870
你没事吧
Are you okay?

264
00:15:32,580 --> 00:15:34,030
我去叫医生
I'll get the doctor up here.

265
00:15:34,820 --> 00:15:36,270
不必了  过一会儿就好
Don't do that. It'll pass.

266
00:15:38,050 --> 00:15:39,160
幻痛而已
Phantom pain.

267
00:15:48,260 --> 00:15:50,240
你知道我来时想做什么吗
You know what I dreamed of when I came here?

268
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:53,610
徒手掐死你
Choking you with my bare hands.

269
00:16:05,660 --> 00:16:07,640
默罕默德先生  你可以恨我
Mr. Mahmoud, you may hate me.

270
00:16:08,280 --> 00:16:10,400
