But here's the reality:

272
00:16:13,880 --> 00:16:18,650
每天我必须做出我但愿是正确的决定
I must make decisions every day that I hope are just.

273
00:16:18,970 --> 00:16:22,210
我也不能一直明辨是非
I don't know right from wrong all the time.

274
00:16:22,210 --> 00:16:23,670
我倒希望我能
I wish I did.

275
00:16:25,300 --> 00:16:27,740
但我决不能优柔寡断
But what I can't be is indecisive.

276
00:16:28,210 --> 00:16:32,460
《古兰经》中说  "夺一无辜之人性命
It says in the Qur'an: "The taking of one innocent life

277
00:16:33,190 --> 00:16:35,450
如了结全人类之性命"
is like the taking of all mankind."

278
00:16:36,410 --> 00:16:40,930
