The next time you wield it... I hope you'll think twice.

291
00:17:32,440 --> 00:17:34,670
一定会的  密查姆
Yes, of course. Meechum!

292
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:36,970
先生  怎么了
Yes, sir?

293
00:17:37,290 --> 00:17:38,850
把默罕默德先生送出去
You show Mr. Mahmoud out.

294
00:17:44,180 --> 00:17:46,590
