Two months of random sampling across the country.

295
00:17:46,590 --> 00:17:49,440
不到所有可用数据的千分之一
Less than a tenth of a percent of all incoming data.

296
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:50,240
怎么这么少
Why so little?

297
00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:52,280
你知道我们监视着多少个摄像机吗
You have any idea how many cameras we monitor?

298
00:17:52,280 --> 00:17:54,710
华盛顿所有主机的CPU核心份额
The CPU core quota of every mainframe in Washington

299
00:17:54,710 --> 00:17:56,300
