他们肯定有口昼夜不停煮花生的锅
They must have a pot boiling 'round the clock.

331
00:19:11,740 --> 00:19:14,080
露丝现在让我吃甘蓝脆片
Ruth has me eating kale crisps now.

332
00:19:14,080 --> 00:19:17,490
